install dependencies with ruby-gems:

sudo gem install eventmachine
sudo gem install rspec

# on the 1.9 branch, you need this gem to detect encodings from irc users
sudo gem install icu-chardet-ffi

rake spec # to run tests

edit bin/bot.conf.example, and save it to file bot.conf
to run: bin/fbsdbot.rb /path/to/config/fbsdbot.conf
